632
00:39:13,640 --> 00:39:14,680
I have already said,

633
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,480
twelve men

634
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:19,600
is my limit.

635
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:24,960
Shall we begin?

636
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,600
I advise you

637
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,080
